        plymouth (<< 0.9.0-7),
        bash-completion (<< 1:2.1),
Description: /dev/ and hotplug management daemon
 eudev is a daemon which dynamically creates and removes device nodes from
 /dev/, handles hotplug events and loads drivers at boot time.

